    <item>
      <title>加巴德称自己不是任何人竞逐高级间谍职位的“傀儡”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/gabbard-says-she-s-no-one-s-puppet-in-bid-for-top-spy-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔尔西·加巴德表示，她拒绝成为任何人的“傀儡”，并承诺结束所谓的情报武器化，这是她定于周四在下一任国家情报总监的确认听证会上发表的准备好的讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/gabbard-says-she-s-no-one-s-puppet-in-bid-for-top-spy-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利国会最终批准重大养老金改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/chile-congress-gives-final-backing-to-long-sought-pension-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国会最终批准了一项改革，该改革将提高现有和未来退休人员的养老金，在政府做出重大让步之后，总统加布里埃尔·博里奇获得了一场苦乐参半的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/chile-congress-gives-final-backing-to-long-sought-pension-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 22:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
